Reka tugende

Hamwe n'izuru ryanjye ...

... Ndahumurirwa amasogisi yanduye.

... Ndahumurirwa indabyo nziza.

Hamwe n'amaso yanjye ...

... Ndabona igipirizo kiri guhuhwa n'umuyaga.

... Ndabona injangwe yishimye.

Hamwe n'akanwa kanjye ...

... Ndumva urwunyunyu rw'umwunyu w'inyanja.

... Ndyohewe n'umutobe uryoshye.

Ukuboko kwanjye ...

... Mfashe ukuboko.
